# CISC-L2-000040 - Denial of Service (DOS) - QoS - Remediation
class-map match-all C2_VOICE
 match ip dscp 47
class-map match-all VOICE
 match ip dscp ef
class-map match-all VIDEO
 match ip dscp af41
class-map match-all PREFERRED_DATA
 match ip dscp af33

policy-map QOS_POLICY_SWITCHPORT
 class C2_VOICE
  priority level 1 10
 class VOICE
  priority level 2 15
 class VIDEO
  bandwidth percent 25 
 class PREFERRED_DATA
  bandwidth percent 25 
 class class-default
  bandwidth percent 25 
